PrecisAuthority for the Port of Quebec Corporation to enter into an Agreement which will amend the Lease held by Intertank-IMTT Inc. with respect to a piece of waterfront land, in order to provide the lessee with two renewal options of ten years each and thereby bring the full term of the lease to a total potential tenure of forty years.
